'''Douglas "Doug" Petrie''' is an [[Wikipedia:Americans|American]] television writer, producer, and director whose credits include [[Wikipedia:Buffy the Vampire Slayer|''Buffy the Vampire Slayer'']], [[Wikipedia:CSI: Crime Scene Investigation|''CSI: Crime Scene Investigation'']], [[Wikipedia:Pushing Daisies|''Pushing Daisies'']], and [[Wikipedia:Tru Calling|''Tru Calling'']].

Petrie wrote [[Star Wars (1998) 27|''Star Wars'' (1998) 27]]. He also co-wrote the ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' episode "[[Death Trap]]."

